{
  "texts": [
    "The overall subject of IoT security was also examined.",
    "Furthermore, Reference [65] reviewed IoT security challenges before suggesting the blockchain as a potential solution to these problems.",
    "They also talked about how IoT and blockchain may work together.",
    "Furthermore, Reference [66] the authors presented a smart contract as a solution to address confidentiality and security issues in IoT systems and enable safe interactions between IoT devices.",
    "By utilizing blockchain technology, their approach enables decentralization of access control, authentication, and payments."
  ]
}